{
  "stem": "11499.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 18.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we bought tickets on the-- on a streamer going to Jozefow, near Lublin.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we-- we left Warsaw, I think 10 or 11 friends.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we came to Jozefow, about five friends split right away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They went their way some place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know where they-- what happened to them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know if they're alive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We-- we stayed in the city of Jozefow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't-- couldn't find out where the partisan is.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So after a few weeks, we found out that the partisans are forming in-- in-- in a village, [POLISH], also near-- not far from Lublin.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We went there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we found a man with a little beard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was the commandant of the-- of the group.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The group's name was [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "His-- the man's name was [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Prokhovnik ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Jagosz ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Corchinsky ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he told us this story, that he was a fighter in-- in Spain, against Franco, in 1936.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And now he's forming a partisan group.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we got the partis-- when we went to the partisan-- That were Poles, not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they were non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Poles.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were about five of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we came in also, we are five Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had no guns.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had no money, nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the first thing, he told us we have to get guns.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he found out, through some people in the-- in the village-- we used to live-- we used to stay in the village, with different farmers, in-- how do you say [POLISH]?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Silo-- like silos.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to stay there, under the-- the straw.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Barn-- on the barn.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So one day, they found that one farmer has a gun.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went to the farmer to get-- to buy the gun from him.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
